Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:25.09,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c4720E8\t(730,980,\3cDF994B)}七転八倒で到着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:28.16,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3cDF994B}既存理論でカクメイ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:31.98,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3cDF994B\t(1200,1400,\3c4720E8)}誰もが予測不能の連鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:34.83,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c993A1E}虚ろう瞳に映る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:37.91,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c993A1E\t(1800,2100,\3c25CAE3)}有象無象は御免
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:41.78,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c25CAE3\t(450,520,\3c2C1C95)}この世の理、手繰って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:44.24,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心中 警戒 絶後 消失 如来像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:46.58,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}虚構 徹頭 徹尾 真実 風来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:51.05,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c4F1D73}モノノケトケモノ ヒトも、割と同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:55.82,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c4F1D73}今、走る言葉がつまづいても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:02:01.31,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3cAC2846}くだらない話でもちゃんと聞いてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:06.30,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}例え細くてもほどけないように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:09.92,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c691F3D}不確かな未来でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:12.10,KYO OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c691F3D\t(1150,1250,\3c2C1C95)}掴んで撃ち砕け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:25.09,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c4720E8\t(730,980,\3cDF994B)}跌跌撞撞地抵达这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:28.16,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3cDF994B}以现存理论发动革命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:31.98,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3cDF994B\t(1200,1400,\3c4720E8)}无可预知的蝴蝶效应
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:34.83,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c993A1E}无视那空洞的瞳中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:37.91,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c993A1E\t(1800,2100,\3c25CAE3)}映出的虚妄之形骸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:41.78,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c25CAE3\t(450,520,\3c2C1C95)}只将此世真理攫取于手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:44.24,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心中 警戒 绝后 消失 如来像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:46.58,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}虚构 彻头 彻尾 真实 风来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:51.05,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c4F1D73}无论鬼怪或妖魔 都与人类无甚区别
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:55.82,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c4F1D73}即使这激扬的话语始终难以传达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:02:01.31,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3cAC2846}也请你仔细听听这些徒然的遐想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:06.30,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}哪怕是只存在细微可能性的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:09.92,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c691F3D}也定会被我们掌握手中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:12.10,KYO OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\3c691F3D\t(1150,1250,\3c2C1C95)}打破世间的虚实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:43.57,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}どこへ行こうか　夢から覚めたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:51.90,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}サファイアの夜　なまぬるい風　潜めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:23:01.14,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}真っ暗なほどに　きれいな瞳が瞬く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:09.12,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}そっと抱き寄せて　優しい獣の声で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:11.16,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}You can do, we can do, try
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.35,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}お遊びのまま　いじらしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:19.99,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}君らしく暴れて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:24.26,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}ふざけないなんて　つまらない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:28.93,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}僕ららしく踊らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.65,KYO EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}I'll save the last dance for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:43.57,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}从梦境醒来后  我们将要前往何方？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:51.90,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}迎着温蕴的风  销声匿迹在蓝宝石般的午夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:23:01.14,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}如深渊般动人的双瞳  迸射着光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:09.12,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}让我将你悄然揽至身畔  如野兽般柔情低语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:11.16,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}You  can  do,  we  can  do,  try
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.35,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}就这样玩世不恭  这样楚楚可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:19.99,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}释放仅属于你的狂野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:24.26,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}若不纵情喧嚣  又有何乐趣可言？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:28.93,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}舞出属于你我的风采吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.65,KYO EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur2}I'll save the last dance for you
